headline: Q3 Rundown: Textron (NYSE:TXT) Vs Other Aerospace Stocks
summary: Quarterly earnings results are a good time to check in on a company’s progress, especially compared to its peers in the same sector. Today we are looking at Textron (NYSE:TXT) and the best and worst performers in the aerospace industry.
